title: PK - KW Converter v1.0
description:
PK - KW Converter is a free tool to calculate easily from PK to KW and fro KW to PK.
How to use? You have to fill in the first field KW or PK and then simply click on the converter button.
You will see the calculated result in the next field on the right side of the window.
This is how simply this tool is.

The reason for this application?
I don't know, it was fun to make it and if someone think it's use-full, that make me happy.
